[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/overcalls"]
[Student "S"]
{NORTH has 12 points and a good enough suit to overcall 1\H.

SOUTH has 9 points with a good \D stopper. She bids 1NT.

NORTH has nothing more to say, and lets SOUTH play 1NT.}

